divs: sighting details06\02\10 at about 9:30 a.m . i was stopped at a light on rt 441 off of 490 in brighton; i was facing east when i saw 2 perfectly round clouds. the sky was blue and there were large billowing clouds which made the smaller round clouds really stand out in comparison. the 2 round clouds began to dissipate revealing 2 silver objects, saucer in shape and the size of jet fighters. one suddenly shot towards the south in a bright flash of light, the other did the same but took off north. i'm not a pilot so i can't state distance but to me the objects were not that far away.

Summary: 2 UFOs in 2 very round clouds which dissipated revealing 2 discs; size of jet fighters
